#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.tensordot.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.tensordot"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:1 of
msgid "Compute tensor dot product along specified axes for tensors >= 1-D."
msgstr "计算沿指定轴的张量点积，适用于维度大于等于1的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:3 of
msgid ""
"Given two tensors (arrays of dimension greater than or equal to one), `a`"
" and `b`, and an array_like object containing two array_like objects, "
"``(a_axes, b_axes)``, sum the products of `a`'s and `b`'s elements "
"(components) over the axes specified by ``a_axes`` and ``b_axes``. The "
"third argument can be a single non-negative integer_like scalar, ``N``; "
"if it is such, then the last ``N`` dimensions of `a` and the first ``N`` "
"dimensions of `b` are summed over."
msgstr ""
"给定两个张量（维度大于等于一的数组），`a` 和 `b`，以及一个包含两个 array_"
"like 对象的 array_like 对象 ``(a_axes, b_axes)``，对 `a` 和 `b` 的元素（"
"分量）在由 ``a_axes`` 和 ``b_axes`` 指定的轴上求和。第三个参数可以是一个"
"非负整数标量 ``N``；如果是这样，则对 `a` 的最后 ``N`` 个维度和 `b` 的前 `"
"`N`` 个维度求和。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:12
#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:14 of
msgid "Tensors to \"dot\"."
msgstr "要进行“点积”的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:16 of
msgid ""
"* integer_like   If an int N, sum over the last N axes of `a` and the "
"first N axes   of `b` in order. The sizes of the corresponding axes must "
"match. * (2,) array_like   Or, a list of axes to be summed over, first "
"sequence applying to `a`,   second to `b`. Both elements array_like must "
"be of the same length."
msgstr ""
"* integer_like   如果是一个整数 N，则依次对 `a` 的最后 N 个轴和 `b` 的前 "
"N 个轴求和。相应轴的大小必须匹配。 * (2,) array_like   或者，一个包含要被"
"求和的轴的列表，第一个序列应用于 `a`，第二个序列应用于 `b`。这两个 array_"
"like 元素的长度必须相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:17 of
msgid ""
"integer_like If an int N, sum over the last N axes of `a` and the first N"
" axes of `b` in order. The sizes of the corresponding axes must match."
msgstr ""
"integer_like 如果是一个整数 N，则依次对 `a` 的最后 N 个轴和 `b` 的前 N 个"
"轴求和。相应轴的大小必须匹配。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:20 of
msgid ""
"(2,) array_like Or, a list of axes to be summed over, first sequence "
"applying to `a`, second to `b`. Both elements array_like must be of the "
"same length."
msgstr ""
"(2,) array_like 或者，一个包含要被求和的轴的列表，第一个序列应用于 `a`，"
"第二个序列应用于 `b`。这两个 array_like 元素的长度必须相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`dot`, :py:obj:`einsum`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:28 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:29 of
msgid "Three common use cases are:"
msgstr "三种常见的使用场景是："

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:31 of
msgid "``axes = 0`` : tensor product :math:`a\\otimes b`"
msgstr "``axes = 0``：张量积 :math:`a\\otimes b`"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:32 of
msgid "``axes = 1`` : tensor dot product :math:`a\\cdot b`"
msgstr "``axes = 1``：张量点积 :math:`a\\cdot b`"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:33 of
msgid "``axes = 2`` : (default) tensor double contraction :math:`a:b`"
msgstr "``axes = 2``：（默认）张量双收缩 :math:`a:b`"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:35 of
msgid ""
"When `axes` is integer_like, the sequence for evaluation will be: first "
"the -Nth axis in `a` and 0th axis in `b`, and the -1th axis in `a` and "
"Nth axis in `b` last."
msgstr ""
"当 `axes` 是 integer_like 时，计算顺序是：首先 `a` 的第 -N 个轴和 `b` 的"
"第 0 个轴，最后是 `a` 的第 -1 个轴和 `b` 的第 N 个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.linalg.tensordot.tensordot:39 of
msgid ""
"When there is more than one axis to sum over - and they are not the last "
"(first) axes of `a` (`b`) - the argument `axes` should consist of two "
"sequences of the same length, with the first axis to sum over given first"
" in both sequences, the second axis second, and so forth."
msgstr ""
"当有多个轴需要求和时，且这些轴不是 `a`（`b`）的最后（前）轴时，参数 `axes"
"` 应该包含两个相同长度的序列，第一个序列中的第一个轴和第二个序列中的"
"第一个轴对应，第二个轴对应第二个，依此类推。"

